        <item>
            <title>《GTA 6》2025 年推出各平台但未有 PC　Fans 估计各版本售价图</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/gta6-2025-on-ps5-xbox-x-s/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gta6-2025-on-ps5-xbox-x-s</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/gta6-2025-on-ps5-xbox-x-s/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:50:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[grand theft auto]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Grand Theft Auto VI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[rockstar]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Take-Two]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208711</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>距离《GTA 5》首发经已逾 10 年，游戏开发商的母公司 Take-Two 日前终于发布官方新闻稿确认《GTA 6》将于 2025 年内首先在 PS5、Xbox Series X|S 两大家用机推出，不过暂时尚未公布有关 PC 的细节。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_73061"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QdBZY2fkU-0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Rockstar 在香港时间今日早上 7 点于 YouTube 上发布了《GTA 6》第一条预告片。预告片中可见 GTA 6 将采用以佛罗里达迈亚密为原型的 Vice City 作游戏地图。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲预告片中可见大大的「VICE」字样</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>双主角设计 + 首次有女性主角</h2><p>预告中同时亦可见有一男一女，相信是游戏主角。如属实的话这次是 GTA 系列首次有女性担任主角。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>更多可进入建筑物 + 打劫系统更完善</h2><p>知名游戏资讯网站《Dexerto》早前曾报道指，网上流传一份有关《GTA 6》的爆料文件。文件中表示《GTA 6》比以往全系列的 GTA 游戏拥有更多可进入建筑物，其中包括酒吧、当舖、脱衣舞俱乐部、超市、商店及部分住宅单位。据《Dexerto》报道指，以上种种可进入建筑物均是为「打劫」系统而设。据悉《GTA 6》的打劫系统将会比上一代更强。Rockstar 官方上载的预告片亦有一男一女角色蒙面进入商店打劫的画面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/gta-6-buildings-leak-694x398.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="398" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/gta-6-buildings-leak-694x398.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/gta-6-buildings-leak.jpg 726w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲官方上传的预告显示一对蒙面男女持枪进入商店的画面</p><h2>传地图比《GTA 5》大 1.75 倍</h2><p>另外据爆料网站《High on Cinemaa》表示，与《GTA 5》Los Santos 的地图相比，《GTA 6》Vice City 的地图大了将近 1.75 倍。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GTA-6-Full-Map-Leak-and-Comparison-With-GTA-5-694x519.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="519" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GTA-6-Full-Map-Leak-and-Comparison-With-GTA-5-694x519.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GTA-6-Full-Map-Leak-and-Comparison-With-GTA-5.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左边为《GTA 6》地图，右边为《GTA 5》地图<br />
图片来源：<a href="https://highoncinemaa.com/high-on-gaming/gta-6-full-map-leak-and-comparison-with-gta-5/16670/">High on Cinemaa</a></p><p>Reddit 用户 @LivingSignificant555 就将两张地图重叠了起来（较深色部分位 GTA 6，较浅色部分为 GTA 5）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208728" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下载-1-584x580.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下载-1-584x580.jpg 584w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下载-1-907x900.jpg 907w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下载-1-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下载-1-768x762.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下载-1.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 584px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左边为《GTA 6》地图，右边为《GTA 5》地图<br />
图片来源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/GTA6/comments/16zbcqi/gta_v_map_size_vs_gta_vi_map_size/">LivingSignificant555@Reddit</a></p><h2>Fans 估计售价图：最平 69.99、最贵 199.99 美元</h2><p>虽然现阶段 Take-Two 尚未公布售价，但有《GTA 6》的拥趸就已经为 Rockstar 制作好售价图。<a href="https://twitter.com/GTAVI_Countdown">@GTAVI_Countdown</a> e 就在 X （前称 Twitter）上发布了自己制作的售价图。@GTAVI_Countdown 预想 GTA6 会有 3 个价钱，最平的 《GTA 6》仅包含单机及 Online 版本，其预想售价为 69.99 美元；最贵的版本除了有单机、Online 版本外，亦包含了 2 位主角的 20 吋 figure、向前代 GTA Vice City 主角 Tommy Vercetti 致敬的 GTA 6 Online 游戏服装、OST、游戏美术设定书册、GTA 6 实体地图及 10,000,000 GTA Online 游戏货币。不知道官方会否参考 @GTAVI_Countdown 的模式售卖 《GTA 6》呢？真正价钱及版本尚要等待官方公布。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-694x466.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-694x466.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-1280x860.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-768x516.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-1536x1032.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.take2games.com/ir/news/rockstar-games-announces-grand-theft-auto-vi-coming-2025">Take2Games</a>、<a href="https://highoncinemaa.com/high-on-gaming/gta-6-full-map-leak-and-comparison-with-gta-5/16670/">High on Cinemaa</a>、<a href="https://hothardware.com/news/gta6-map-size-hype">Hot Hardware</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/GTAVI_Countdown">GTAVI_Countdown@X</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gy