            <title>Cybertruck 车内电线用少一半铜，总布线量比同类车少 77%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/cybertruck-use-less-copper-for-wire/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cybertruck-use-less-copper-for-wire</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/cybertruck-use-less-copper-for-wire/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 07:44:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Cybertruck]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Cybertruck]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[纯电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208698</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>传统汽车的电线布局一般非常复杂，线束非常庞大，因为往往它们会将每一个零件独立分开自己一组电线，以连接到中央电子控制器（Electronic Control Unit，ECU）方能够发挥作用。不论是车内音响喇叭、冷气、开关、甚至任何一组传感器、任何一个按钮，全部均需要独立连接至 ECU。</p><p>而 Tesla 的 Cybertruck 把整个电线布局系统化整为零，从头开始设计。Tesla Cybertruck 不再以独立电线连接各个部件。取而代之的是， Cybertruck 采用「菊花链（daisy-chain）」形式把以太网线与 48v 电源以及连接车内每个组件的数据线连接在同一条电缆上。现时 Cybertruck 的车内电脑可以穿过喇叭、车窗、氛围灯、直接利用同一条电线连接到门把手。每一个设备和组件都会持续监察数据流动，直接获得与其操作有关的指令。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208702" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GAgVmhpXIAADF36-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GAgVmhpXIAADF36-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GAgVmhpXIAADF36-768x416.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GAgVmhpXIAADF36.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/GAgVmhpXIAADF36?format=jpg&amp;name=medium">cybrtrkguy@X</a></p><p>据 <a href="https://twitter.com/cybrtrkguy">cybrtrkguy@X</a> 表示，Tesla 通过以上方式，能够减低 Cybertruck 的总布线量 77%，而其所用于电线上的铜更只有传统汽车电线布局的一半。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1208703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GAgVnrtWcAAEKdH.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="295" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/GAgVnrtWcAAEKdH?format=jpg&amp;name=small">cybrtrkguy@X</a></p><p>上月 Tesla 官方宣布 Cybertruck 将于香港时间 12 月 1 日凌晨于美国德州超级工厂开始全球正式交付。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/cybrtrkguy/status/1731658374775771297">cybrtrkguy@X</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>====</p><h2>unwire learn 推出:</h2><p><strong>独门 AI 用法助你工作及创业课程</strong><br /><a href="https://learn.unwire.hk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&lt;按此报名&gt;</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/cybertruck-use-less-copper-for-wire/life-tech/auto/">Cybertruck 车内电线用少一半铜，总布线量比同类车少 77%</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
